33
00:04:12,950 --> 00:04:15,470
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="40">I can exist anywhere.</font>

34
00:04:15,470 --> 00:04:20,330
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="40">No matter where my body is, I can send my consciousness anywhere I want.</font>

35
